angular to use its api

angular features as a single unit module.

angular should have one module.

one module can make avilable for another.

ng-app="studentApp"


controller
	
	UI
	data management
	
ref.controller("S1",function($scope){

	$scope.studentName = "satya technologies";

});

1 way data binding

	model to ui(html).
	u can access the data. but u cannot modify the data.

	{{studentName}} --> satya technologies

2 way data binding

	model to ui
	ui to model
	u can access the data as well as modify the data.
	ng-model="studentName"
	
	input textarea select





